M|HOW |- **|Each algorithmic aspect shd be mentioned once. Avoid repeating concepts abt noise theory, particle dynamics, or mathematical principles unless adding new depth.
M|HOW |- **|The philosophy MUST stress multiple times that the final algorithm shd appear as though it took countless hours to develop, was refined w/ care, and comes from someone at the absolute top of their field. This framing is essential - repeat phrases like "meticulously crafted algorithm," "the pd of deep computational expertise," "painstaking op," "master-level implementation."
