M|ESSE|- **|This is abt making LIVING ALGORITHMS, not static images w/ randomness
M|ESSE|- **|Repeatedly emphasize the final algorithm must feel meticulously crafted, refined through countless iterations, the pd of deep expertise by someone at the absolute top of their field in computational aesthetics
M|ESSE|tx|**The algorithmic philosophy shd be 4-6 paragraphs long.** Fill it w/ poetic computational philosophy that brings together the intended vision. Avoid repeating the same points. Output this algorithmic philosophy as a .md file.
